Double Active Baking Powder, also called double acting baking powder, releases carbon dioxide when exposed to moisture and heat, causing doughs and batters to rise. It is all natural and contains no aluminum.

Perfect a variety of your signature baked goods with double acting baking powder! Primarily used as a leavening agent in dough and batter products that require rapid aeration, this double acting baking powder is ideal for producing superb quick rise breads.
